      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUACAMOLE IRISH (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (17.02) at this track behind Hot Summer Sky in a Grade 5. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Makes plenty of appeal. LAVERS GINNY (2) lines up chasing another win after scoring over 300m at this track in 17.01, set up by a brilliant early sectional. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Leading chance again. GLAMOROUS JEWEL (8) was safely held in tougher company last start at this track, but prior to that won by 2.25 lengths at this track (17.03) beating Thai Butterfly in a Grade 5 on May 22. Has ability and is one of the better chances. SWEET CANNELLONI (1) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
